title: >>> A Women's WAR
body_text:
The time nears once again for the next big match-up ...
DIANA DIBUCCIO

Height 5'4"
Current Residence: Allentown, NJ
Debut: DODGEBALL DAY 1

SARA DECUIR
Born November 11th, 1985
Height 5'4"
Current Residence: Wall, NJ
Debut: DODGEBALL XONE

Which female will rule the dodgeball world!??! Witness DODGEGALL 46, June 30th, to find out.
*Anyone think about forming a stable? If you are confused, simply read the entry before this one.
